title: Lyft Reports Earnings, Looking Ahead To Uber
itunes:title: Lyft Reports Earnings, Looking Ahead To Uber
description:
Mandeep Singh, Senior Tech Industry Analyst for Bloomberg Intelligence, discusses Lyft and Uber earnings. Jennifer Epstein, Political Reporter for Bloomberg News, talks about President Biden's new eviction ban. Thaddeus Malik, Partner and Chair of the Global Mergers and Acquisitions practice at Paul Hastings, discusses the M&A market. Kate El-Hillow, Global Chief Investment Officer at Russell Investments discusses markets. Hosted by Paul Sweeney and Matt Miller. (Kailey Leinz fills in for Paul Sweeney)
